%% Diagram: Hybrid ABR decision loop
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    START[Segment downloaded] --> EWMA[Update throughput EWMA<br/>recent N segments]
    START --> BUF[Read buffer level<br/>seconds queued]
    EWMA --> COMBINE[Combine signals]
    BUF --> COMBINE
    COMBINE --> DECIDE{Buffer state}
    DECIDE -->|under low watermark<br/>< 5s| DROP[Drop to lowest rung<br/>do not adapt up]
    DECIDE -->|low to mid<br/>5-15s| THROUGHPUT[Throughput-dominant<br/>0.7 x EWMA cap]
    DECIDE -->|mid to high<br/>15-30s| HYBRID[BOLA-style utility<br/>buffer-weighted]
    DECIDE -->|near full<br/>> 30s| HOLD[Hold or step up<br/>if next rung fits]
    DROP --> EMIT[Choose next rung]
    THROUGHPUT --> EMIT
    HYBRID --> EMIT
    HOLD --> EMIT
    EMIT --> CONSTRAIN[Apply constraints<br/>min dwell 10s<br/>max drop 2 rungs]
    CONSTRAIN --> NEXT[Request next segment]
